    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 1. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in the CPB operating envelope described in the bound requirement (https://uofa.net/morrison/req/cpb-hemolysis-mrl2) and supported by the validation evidence bound to this assessment.",
